understand the universe.

00:02:35.830 --> 00:02:37.480 align:middle line:84%
Hermetic principle
of correspondence

00:02:37.480 --> 00:02:41.380 align:middle line:84%
tells us, as the
inner so the outer.

00:02:41.380 --> 00:02:46.180 align:middle line:84%
The numerology associated
with the Hermit is number 9,

00:02:46.180 --> 00:02:50.560 align:middle line:84%
and 9 is the end of the
numerical series of 1 to 9.

00:02:50.560 --> 00:02:53.470 align:middle line:84%
So 9 is the culmination
of everything

00:02:53.470 --> 00:02:55.270 align:middle line:90%
that has gone on before it.

00:02:55.270 --> 00:02:57.580 align:middle line:90%
It's the completion of a cycle.

00:02:57.580 --> 00:03:01.360 align:middle line:84%
We're coming to the end
of one stage, the descent,

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:03.580 align:middle line:84%
and we're about to
begin a new stage

00:03:03.580 --> 00:03:08.790 align:middle line:84%
at the turning point, which is
then followed by an ascension.

00:03:08.790 --> 00:03:12.280 align:middle line:10%
And so 9 represents
the conclusion,

00:03:12.280 --> 00:03:15.040 align:middle line:10%
and it ties together all
the different key elements,

00:03:15.040 --> 00:03:16.870 align:middle line:10%
the lessons, the
insights that have been

00:03:16.870 --> 00:03:20.015 align:middle line:10%
gained from the previous cycle.

00:03:20.015 --> 00:03:23.220 align:middle line:10%
Now, with this ending, there
are some weighty aspects

00:03:23.220 --> 00:03:26.430 align:middle line:10%
that come with 9, and
these are balanced, though,

00:03:26.430 --> 00:03:28.830 align:middle line:10%
by the fool, which
is 0, which is

00:03:28.830 --> 00:03:31.480 align:middle line:10%
the gateway to any new cycle.

00:03:31.480 --> 00:03:36.030 align:middle line:84%
